            "description": "The UTSUNOMIYA JAPAN CUP CYCLE ROAD RACE Organising Committee will be livestreaming their event online. A total of 19 teams with 114 riders are set to compete, featuring UCI WorldTeams and globally recognized international teams. The event will take place in UTSUNOMIYA, Japan on October 10, 2025. Among the participants, sponsors include SUBARU LAYBACK.",
