            "title": "Renalys completes primary endpoint data collection for Phase III trial of sparsentan for IgA nephropathy in Japan.",
            "id": "15d5592d-ffe0-460a-83d7-4630a83a83fb",
            "description": "Tokyo's Renalys Pharma, Inc. disclosed today the successful conclusion of data gathering for the primary endpoint in the Phase III clinical trial of sparsentan (development code: RE-021) aimed at treating IgA nephropathy in Japan. The company, headquartered in Chuo-ku, Tokyo, stated that they have finalized data collection for the study. This news showcases a significant milestone in the research, emphasizing progress in the development of potential treatments for IgA nephropathy.",
